  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.physletb.2004.11.060.pdf_2_23",
    "text": "Suppose Eq. (5) is valid only up to a cutoff frequency Vc, due to new but as yet unknown physics. How might we determine vc? We propose using estimates of the dark energy density to place an upper limit on the value calculated from Eq. (7).",
